00141 void DATDataTest::SubgridTest()
00142 {
00143         FGridCoords grid;
00144         grid.lowerleft.x = 1.0f;
00145         grid.lowerleft.y = 1.2f;
00146         grid.lowerright.x = 11.0f;
00147         grid.lowerright.y = 14.2f;
00148         grid.upperright.x = 111.0f;
00149         grid.upperright.y = 114.2f;
00150         grid.upperleft.x = 1001.0f;
00151         grid.upperleft.y = 1200.2f;
00152 
00153         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data->GetSubgridCnt() == 0);
00154 
00155         data->AddSubgrid(DATData::GridOK, (FRegion)grid);
00156         FGridCoords grid2 = grid;
00157         grid2.lowerleft.x = 2.0f;
00158         data->AddSubgrid(DATData::GridManualAdjust, (FRegion)grid2);
00159 
00160         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data->GetSubgridCnt() == 2);
00161 
00162         FGridCoords grid3 = (FGridCoords)data->GetSubgrid(0);
00163         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(grid3.lowerleft.x == 1.0f);
00164         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(grid3.lowerleft.y == 1.2f);
00165         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(grid3.lowerright.x == 11.0f);
00166         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(grid3.lowerright.y == 14.2f);
00167         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(grid3.upperright.x == 111.0f);
00168         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(grid3.upperright.y == 114.2f);
00169         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(grid3.upperleft.x == 1001.0f);
00170         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(grid3.upperleft.y == 1200.2f);
00171         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data->GetSubgridStatus(0) == DATData::GridOK);
00172 
00173         FGridCoords grid4 = (FGridCoords)data->GetSubgrid(1);
00174         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(grid4.lowerleft.x == 2.0f);
00175         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data->GetSubgridStatus(1) == DATData::GridManualAdjust);
00176 
00177         data->ClearSubgrids();
00178 
00179         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data->GetSubgridCnt() == 0);
00180 }

00204 void DATDataTest::FindGridAlignmentAlgorithmParameterTest()
00205 {
00206         ParameterNameValueType nvt;
00207         nvt.SetName(L"Nirvana");
00208         nvt.SetValueInt32(1234);
00209         data->AddGridAlignmentAlgorithmParameter(nvt);
00210         nvt.SetName(L"Hole");
00211         nvt.SetValueText(L"OU812");
00212         data->AddGridAlignmentAlgorithmParameter(nvt);
00213 
00214         ParameterNameValueType nvtResult;
00215         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data->FindGridAlignmentAlgorithmParameter(L"Hole", nvtResult));
00216         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvtResult.GetValueText() == L"OU812");
00217         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data->FindGridAlignmentAlgorithmParameter(L"Nirvana", nvtResult));
00218         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvtResult.GetValueInt32() == 1234);
00219         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data->FindGridAlignmentAlgorithmParameter(L"Missing", nvtResult) == false);
00220 }
